metadata.name: The Theater
metadata.description:
The Chicago Theater, originally known as the Balaban and Katz Chicago Theatre, is a landmark theater located on North State Street in the Loop area of Chicago, Illinois, United States. Built in 1921, the Chicago Theatre is one of the most popular tourist attractions and theaters in the region.

Taken on canon eos r6
